  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      35 patients with multiple sclerosis have been enrolled in a previous study to record and
      analyze gait parameters.

      This study aims to enroll gender and and matched healthy subjects for a control group, to
      compare patients' gait parameters with healthy subjects'.
    </textblock>
